SUMMARY:Easter Sunday Walk - Pickering Waterfront
DESCRIPTION:GTA Hiking & Stuff\nSince the trails are still icy and very mu
 ddy\, we will walk the waterfront trail in Pickering and take in the beaut
 y of the Lake Ontario shoreline and Pickering nuclear plant. We will walk 
 at a moderate pace for 10 kms in 2 hrs or less. The plan will be to walk t
 he paved pathway west towards the Rouge River and back. Our meeting spot w
 ill be the Westshore Community Center parking lot. As of now the forecast 
 is calling for a cloudy day with no rain. Lets hope that doesn't change.\n
 \nCome out for an Easter Sunday walk and make room for your festive family
  dinner.\n\n**Note**\n- Arrive on time! Don't let the group wait for you.\
 n- Know your limits! Choose the hike that matches your fitness level.\n- D
 ress for the conditions.\n- Free Parking\n- No Dogs\n- The hike will be ca
 nceled if the weather doesn't cooperate.\n\n**LEGAL DISCLAIMER AND LIABILI
